# 🧠 The clean comparison (core idea)

| Type        | What it checks                    | Shape                        |
| ----------- | --------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Snapshot    | “Did this exact behavior change?” | single run → saved output    |
| Property    | “Is this always valid?”           | single run → invariant       |
