# 🧠 What “good enough for Phase 3” actually means

Your scoring function should be:

### ✅ Deterministic

### ✅ Cheap

### ✅ Explainable

### ✅ Slightly better than random

### ❌ Not optimized

### ❌ Not learned

### ❌ Not context-aware (yet)

